To use these scripts:

$ cd ~
$ bzr branch lp:~khaeru/+junk/scripts .bin

In ~/.profile, replace:

  # set PATH so it includes user's private bin if it exists
  if [ -d "$HOME/bin" ] ; then
    PATH="$HOME/bin:$PATH"
  fi

...with:

  # set PATH so it includes user's private bin if it exists
  if [ -d "$HOME/.bin" ] ; then
    PATH="$HOME/.bin:$PATH"
  fi

This hides the directory ~/.bin from most views of your home directory,
but leaves the scripts accessible.
